Title:

Simple Java Project on Inheritance and Method Overriding â€“ Swiggy Food Delivery System

Objective:

To design and implement a Java program that demonstrates:

Inheritance: Sharing and extending common behaviors from parent classes.

Method Overriding: Customizing behavior in child classes.

Packages: Organizing classes for clarity and professionalism.











