ğŸ§¾ How to Compile and Run

Open the project in any IDE (Eclipse / IntelliJ / VS Code)
or from terminal:

cd SwiggyProject/src
javac com/swiggy/base/*.java com/swiggy/orders/*.java com/swiggy/main/*.java
java com.swiggy.main.SwiggyApp
